{
  "texts": [
    "The results of deep learning models on KDD Cup-99 presented in Table 6 and Figure 2 provide a comprehensive overview of their performance.",
    "CNN achieved an accuracy of 89.10%, indicating the percentage of correctly classified instances.",
    "Its precision, recall, and F1-score are 87.23%, 85.43%, and 86.31%, respectively.",
    "The LSTM model demonstrated higher accuracy, reaching 92.25%.",
    "The hybrid model (CNN-LSTM) performed exceptionally well, with an accuracy of 95.11%."
  ]
}